metadata.name: Route One: Out the Mud
metadata.description:
A journey filled with plenty of loops and turns.

Encounters on this route are meant to knock you out of the game...

 However, if you face your challenges head on, successfully overcoming the adversities thrown at you and ultimately capturing your goals... Your Character will mold into a master of games... You will become a king among mortals, prepared for any and all things thrown your way!

This painting was made by artist/creative Aaron Chaz in March 2021 and was originally shared to IG (@Livingsmooth_) 03/06/ 2021.

Due to unfortunate circumstances this original painting  no longer exist in the physical world.

Making it exclusively available  on the blockchain.
